cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is about incorporating syntactic information into neural machine translation systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing and computational linguistics. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which suggests categories such as cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves improving translation accuracy, which could fall under categories such as cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition).
